     fhir:div [ fhir:v "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: CodeSystem CRBehaviourCS</b></p><a name=\"CRBehaviourCS\"> </a><a name=\"hcCRBehaviourCS\"> </a><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\"/><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profiles: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/crmi/STU1/StructureDefinition-crmi-shareablecodesystem.html\">CRMI Shareable CodeSystem</a>, <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/crmi/STU1/StructureDefinition-crmi-publishablecodesystem.html\">CRMI Publishable CodeSystem</a></p></div><p>This case-sensitive code system <code>https://dhis2.org/fhir/cancer-registry/CodeSystem/CRBehaviourCS</code> defines the following codes:</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">0<a name=\"CRBehaviourCS-0\"> </a></td><td>Benign (0)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">1<a name=\"CRBehaviourCS-1\"> </a></td><td>Uncertain (1)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2<a name=\"CRBehaviourCS-2\"> </a></td><td>In situ (2)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">3<a name=\"CRBehaviourCS-3\"> </a></td><td>Malignant (3)</td></tr></table></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
